    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, i'm a high school civics teacher and i'm working on a lesson about the 14th amendment. i want to explain the idea of 'substantive due process' to my students, specifically focusing on how it's been a key tool for protecting civil rights. can u draft a short explanation i can use for them?",
